sections.heading: residential real property, defined
sections.text: Complex residential real property means residential property in which the property to be appraised, the form of ownership, or the market conditions are complicated or atypical.SourceLaws 2014, LB717, ยง 6;R.S.Supp.,2014, ยง 76-2211;Laws 2015, LB139, ยง 16;R.S.Supp.,20
